name: Chelsea Lauren | Photographer
bio:

Photographer by night

social_posts.post_text:
OMG I'm 💀 over this insanely cute reel that IG made for me. It really gave me all the feels.  I love sneaking up on my friends with my video and catching their reactions.

😍😍

What a dream last night was!!

Thank you #HFPA for choosing us at @shutterstocknow to be your house photography team for the @goldenglobes !

Had the best morning ever with King Darbin and his faithful attendant @haleyluhoo 😻

Excited for another awards season with @sagawards + @shutterstocknow

First Sundance post!

I was given the incredible opportunity to shoot for the @people / @entertainmentweekly / @shutterstocknow portrait studio presented by @canonusa at @sundanceorg this year!

There will be a few posts -  there are just too many great talents and images to fit into one.

Thank you so much to my incredible team at @shutterstocknow for making this happen: @andreagcollins @sunburnedgoth @timfxplant

More Sundance!

I was given the incredible opportunity to shoot for the @people / @entertainmentweekly / @shutterstocknow portrait studio presented by @canonusa at @sundanceorg this year!

Thank you so much to my incredible team at @shutterstocknow for making this happen: @andreagcollins @sunburnedgoth @timfxplant

What a joy it was to be with @dylanmulvaney as she got ready to attend the Grammy Awards today!

She is one of the most kind, honest and endearing human beings I've ever had the pleasure of calling a friend. I cannot wait to see where her journey leads!❤️
When the undisputed king of parties @vasjmorgan asks you to shoot his GRAMMYS soiree in honor of @ritaora, you do NOT say no!
A few more Sundance portraits from my @shutterstocknow studio for @people  and @entertainmentweekly presented by @canonusa!

Thank you to Santa Barbara International Film Festival for having me shoot the portrait studio for @shutterstocknow. 

This set of images is from the Virtuosos night.

Portraits taken for Santa Barbara International Film Festival. 

Really happy with how these turned out. 💕

Did another studio last night with the wonderful @hollywoodcriticsassociation 🖤

I've been itching to do this for quite some time and I'm so joyful that they allowed me the freedom to get a bit artsy.

@shutterstocknow 
Assistants: @thecaswellian & @carly.rene
Editor: @pickledwally
One more set from last night with the @hollywoodcriticsassociation 😍🖤
Last night I had the honor of shooting the moment the @sagawards winners get their names engraved on their awards... Here are a few favorites 💕

Happy birthday to my fire-hearted beautiful friend, @jaime_king ❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥

We took these in all of 10 minutes just goofing off while she prepared for her birthday festivities.... She's not only a photographer's DREAM, but an incredible friend, mother and warrior human as well.

Here's to many many more years of loving you, James.
I had the most beautiful night with the most beautiful souls supporting @gocampaign for another year!

Had a blast last night doing portraits for @vasjmorgan and Michael Braun's annual Halloween party. 

So many beautiful people and costumes to choose from, it was hard to narrow down! 💕
Last night with Christie's for Sami Hayek's 'Frequency' exhibition opening.

Rockstar by day.
Photographer by night
_
